OL,3,CDomestic abuse survivor supports new
OL,4,Ctoolkit to identify victims
OL,6,F'Nicky' said: "I met the man of my
OL,7,Fdreams, before I knew it I was living
OL,8,Fin a gilded cage.
OL,10,F"I feared for my life constantly, I
OL,11,Flived in a state of fear. I was scared
OL,12,Fall the time and I tried to keep him
OL,13,Fquiet, to keep him happy, but it
OL,14,Fdidn't matter, we'd have a fantastic
OL,15,Fday out somewhere and at the end of
OL,16,Fit, I'd have a punch in the face.
OL,18,F"I had my front teeth punched out and
OL,19,Fa fractured jaw, I'm still in pain
OL,20,Fwith my face now.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
