OL,3,CDomestic abuse survivor supports new
OL,4,Ctoolkit to identify victims
OL,6,F"I was laying on the floor with my
OL,7,Fteeth next to me covered in blood and
OL,8,Fhe kicked me and went to bed."
OL,10,FWhen 'Nicky' was diagnosed with breast
OL,11,Fcancer, the abuse turned financial.
OL,12,FThe diagnosis gave her the courage to
OL,13,Fleave.
OL,15,FShe said: "When you have a diagnosis
OL,16,Flike cancer, it changes your
OL,17,Fperspective. Even though I was going
OL,18,Fthrough chemotherapy on my own, I just
OL,19,Fdidn't want it any more.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
