OL,3,CDomestic abuse survivor supports new
OL,4,Ctoolkit to identify victims
OL,6,F"If I'd had him back, I don't think
OL,7,FI'd be here now."
OL,9,FResearch shows that while domestic
OL,10,Fabuse usually starts before someone is
OL,11,Fdiagnosed with a serious illness, it
OL,12,Foften escalates.
OL,14,FExperts at the University of
OL,15,FSouthampton have evidence that those
OL,16,Fwith life-limiting illnesses, who
OL,17,Fdepend on their partner for help, are
OL,18,Fparticularly vulnerable to domestic
OL,19,Fabuse.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
