OL,3,CDomestic abuse survivor supports new
OL,4,Ctoolkit to identify victims
OL,6,FDr Michelle Myall, Senior Researcher,
OL,7,FUniversity of Southampton, said:
OL,8,F"Illness can be a trigger for abuse
OL,9,Fbut often it pre-dates the illness and
OL,10,Fit can be exacerbated once a diagnosis
OL,11,Fis given."
OL,13,F'Nicky' has helped to launch a
OL,14,Fguidance package, called the DALLI
OL,15,FToolkit, giving professionals the
OL,16,Ftools to identify abuse victims and
OL,17,Frespond.
OL,19,FIt is hoped that the guidance will be
OL,20,Frolled out across the UK and abroad.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
